    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You release an arcane arrow that traces the path of the triggering attack back to your unseen attacker, provided the attacker is in range. That creature must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or be outlined in light until the end of your next turn. While outlined in light, the creature sheds dim light in a 10-foot radius, any attack roll against it is made with advantage if the attacker can see the creature, and the creature can’t benefit from being invisible.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
